OL,3,CMan who murdered couple in their own
OL,4,Chome jailed for life
OL,6,FA man who was found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a couple in their East
OL,8,FSussex home has been sentenced to life
OL,9,Fin prison, with a minimum term of 29
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FDerek Martin struck Chloe Bashford,
OL,13,F30, with a hammer and stabbed her
OL,14,Fbefore killing her husband Joshua
OL,15,FBashford, 33, in Newhaven on 9 June
OL,16,F2023.
