OL,6,FIn a police interview, Martin
OL,7,Fconfessed he had been cleaning a
OL,8,Fwindow at the couple's property when
OL,9,Fhe "just flipped" over a row about
OL,10,Fmoney with Chloe.
OL,12,FHe struck her over the head with a
OL,13,Fhammer then stabbed her to death.
OL,15,FMartin said that Josh arrived home a
OL,16,Fshort while later and saw him with a
OL,17,Fknife in his hand. Josh ran upstairs
OL,18,Fbut was chased by Martin, who
OL,19,Frepeatedly stabbed him then strangled
OL,20,Fhim to death.
