OL,6,FThe 67-year-old, of Moulsecoomb Way,
OL,7,FBrighton, then changed his clothes,
OL,8,Fpicked up the couple's four children
OL,9,Ffrom school, and took them to Costa
OL,10,Fand McDonald's in Newhaven.
OL,12,FDuring this time, he discarded Chloe's
OL,13,Fmobile phone in bushes of the nearby
OL,14,FSainsbury's.
OL,16,FHe returned the children to their
OL,17,Fgrandmother's house - his ex-wife - in
OL,18,FBrighton. He then bought lager from a
OL,19,Fshop in Whitehawk, which he drank on
OL,20,Fthe seafront.
