OL,6,FShortly afterwards, he handed himself
OL,7,Fin at the police station and told
OL,8,Fofficers "I've killed two people".
OL,10,FPolice went to the Bashford's family
OL,11,Fhome, where they discovered the
OL,12,Fcouple's bodies. Martin was then
OL,13,Farrested.
OL,15,FMartin admitted causing the deaths of
OL,16,FChloe and Josh Bashford, but denied
OL,17,Fmurder due to diminished
OL,18,Fresponsibility resulting from a
OL,19,Fdepressive disorder.
