OL,6,FThe court heard Martin and Chloe
OL,7,Fbecame close a couple of years ago.
OL,9,FMartin had been known to Chloe as he
OL,10,Fwas previously married to her mother,
OL,11,Fbut they had divorced some years
OL,12,Fbefore she was born.
OL,14,FWhile Martin was not still in a
OL,15,Frelationship with Chloe's mother, she
OL,16,Freferred to him as "step dad" in a
OL,17,Ftext to her friend the day she died.
OL,19,FWhile he was remanded in custody,
OL,20,FSussex Police issued a public appeal
OL,21,Fto help find Chloe's mobile phone.
