OL,6,FMartin saw the appeal and passed a
OL,7,Fhand-written note to a prison guard,
OL,8,Fwhich confirmed where he had discarded
OL,9,Fthe device.
OL,11,FThis contained vital evidence, which
OL,12,Fwas subsequently used in the trial.
OL,14,FA jury found him guilty of two counts
OL,15,Fof murder on Friday 24 October
OL,16,Ffollowing a three-week trial at Lewes
OL,17,FCrown Court.
