OL,6,FThe trial at Brighton Law Courts was
OL,7,Ftold that the defendant was very close
OL,8,Fto the couple and their four children
OL,9,Fand spent a lot of time at their home.
OL,11,FThe jury unanimously found Martin
OL,12,Fguilty on both counts of murder after
OL,13,Ffive and a half hours deliberation.
OL,15,FMartin, wearing a grey tracksuit,
OL,16,Fshowed no emotion as the verdict was
OL,17,Fread out.
OL,19,FMore to follow.
